(## INTRODUCTION) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Romify is a travel booking web application designed to help users search and book hotels,) Tj
T*
(flights, and buses from one platform. The system also provides authentication, booking history,) Tj
T*
(payment flow, admin management, and a city guide chatbot that suggests popular places when a) Tj
T*
(user enters a city name.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The application is built using Angular for the frontend, Spring Boot for the backend REST API,) Tj
T*
(and MySQL as the database. It follows a modular structure so that each feature, such as hotels,) Tj
T*
(flights, buses, booking, authentication, and administration, can be maintained independently.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## COMPANY PROFILE) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
([Company Name] is an organization that provides software development and technology-based) Tj
T*
(solutions. The company focuses on building reliable, user-friendly, and scalable applications) Tj
T*
(for real-world business needs.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(For this project, the company acted as the development and guidance organization for the Romify) Tj
T*
(travel booking system.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj
T*
() Tj
ET
