BT /F1 10 Tf 50 790 Td 14 TL
(## PROBLEM STATEMENT) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Travellers often need to use multiple platforms to search hotels, flights, buses, and travel-) Tj
T*
(related information. This increases effort, causes confusion, and makes booking management) Tj
T*
(difficult.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The problem is to develop a single travel booking system where users can search hotels,) Tj
T*
(flights, and buses, create bookings, make payment entries, view previous bookings, and get) Tj
T*
(quick place suggestions for selected cities.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## EXISTING SYSTEM AND NEED FOR THE SYSTEM) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(In an existing manual or semi-digital travel booking process, users may need to contact agents) Tj
T*
(or visit separate websites for different services. Booking details may be scattered across) Tj
T*
(different systems, and users may not have one place to view their travel history.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Limitations of Existing System:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Separate platforms for hotel, flight, and bus booking.) Tj
T*
(- Time-consuming comparison of travel options.) Tj
T*
(- No centralized booking history.) Tj
T*
(- Manual dependency on agents for basic travel suggestions.) Tj
T*
(- Difficult administration of hotel, flight, and bus records.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Need for Proposed System:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- A single platform for multiple travel services.) Tj
T*
(- Faster search and booking experience.) Tj
T*
(- Secure login and user-specific booking history.) Tj
T*
(- Admin panel for managing travel inventory.) Tj
T*
(- Chatbot support for city-based place suggestions.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## SCOPE OF THE PROPOSED SYSTEM) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The proposed Romify system covers:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- User registration and login.) Tj
T*
(- Hotel search, listing, detail view, and booking.) Tj
T*
(- Flight search, listing, and booking.) Tj
T*
(- Bus search, listing, and booking.) Tj
T*
(- Booking history for logged-in users.) Tj
ET
endstream
endobj
