(## BRIEF DESCRIPTION OF TECHNOLOGY USED) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Angular: Used to build the single-page frontend application with modules, components, forms,) Tj
T*
(routing, and services.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Spring Boot: Used to build REST APIs for authentication, hotels, flights, buses, and bookings.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(MySQL: Used as the relational database for users, travel products, and bookings.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Spring Security and JWT: Used for secure login and protected APIs.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Hibernate / JPA: Used for object-relational mapping between Java entities and database tables.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(SCSS: Used for styling frontend components.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## SYSTEM ANALYSIS AND DESIGN) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The Romify system is divided into frontend, backend, and database layers. Users interact with) Tj
T*
(Angular screens. Angular services call Spring Boot REST APIs. The backend validates data,) Tj
T*
(applies security rules, performs business logic, and stores data in MySQL.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The main actors are:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Guest User) Tj
T*
(- Registered User) Tj
T*
(- Admin) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The main modules are:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Authentication Module) Tj
T*
(- Hotel Module) Tj
T*
(- Flight Module) Tj
T*
(- Bus Module) Tj
T*
(- Booking Module) Tj
T*
(- Payment Module) Tj
T*
(- Admin Module) Tj
T*
(- Chatbot Module) Tj
ET
