(## SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Functional Requirements) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(| ID | Requirement |) Tj
T*
(|---|---|) Tj
T*
(| FR-01 | The system shall allow users to register with name, email, and password. |) Tj
T*
(| FR-02 | The system shall allow users to log in using email and password. |) Tj
T*
(| FR-03 | The system shall display hotels with filtering by location, rating, price, and sorting. |) Tj
T*
(| FR-04 | The system shall display flights with filtering by source, destination, class, price, and sorting. |) Tj
T*
(| FR-05 | The system shall display buses with filtering by source, destination, bus type, price, and sorting. |) Tj
T*
(| FR-06 | The system shall allow authenticated users to create bookings. |) Tj
T*
(| FR-07 | The system shall allow users to view their booking history. |) Tj
T*
(| FR-08 | The system shall provide a payment screen for booking confirmation workflow. |) Tj
T*
(| FR-09 | The system shall allow admin users to add, update, and delete hotel records. |) Tj
T*
(| FR-10 | The chatbot shall accept a city name and display popular places. |) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Non-Functional Requirements) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(| ID | Requirement |) Tj
T*
(|---|---|) Tj
T*
(| NFR-01 | The user interface should be responsive. |) Tj
T*
(| NFR-02 | APIs should return proper HTTP status codes. |) Tj
T*
(| NFR-03 | Passwords should be stored in encrypted form. |) Tj
T*
(| NFR-04 | Protected APIs should require JWT authentication. |) Tj
T*
(| NFR-05 | The system should be modular and maintainable. |) Tj
T*
(| NFR-06 | Form validation should prevent invalid user input. |) Tj
T*
(| NFR-07 | The system should be easy to deploy in a local environment. |) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## FEASIBILITY STUDY) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Technical Feasibility) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The project is technically feasible because it uses widely available technologies such as) Tj
T*
(Angular, Spring Boot, Java, and MySQL. These technologies support modular development, REST) Tj
T*
(APIs, and secure authentication.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Economic Feasibility) Tj
ET
