T*
() Tj
T*
(- Presentation Layer: Angular components and pages.) Tj
T*
(- Service Layer: Angular services and Spring Boot controllers.) Tj
T*
(- Security Layer: JWT authentication and authorization.) Tj
T*
(- Data Access Layer: Spring Data JPA repositories.) Tj
T*
(- Database Layer: MySQL tables.) Tj
