() Tj
T*
(Frontend Implementation:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Angular modules are used for feature separation.) Tj
T*
(- Components are used for pages such as home, hotel list, flight list, bus list, booking,) Tj
T*
(  payment, and admin dashboard.) Tj
T*
(- Services communicate with REST APIs using HTTP client.) Tj
T*
(- JWT interceptor attaches authentication token to protected API requests.) Tj
T*
(- Shared components include navbar, footer, loader, hotel card, and chatbot.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Backend Implementation:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Spring Boot exposes REST APIs.) Tj
T*
(- Controllers handle requests and responses.) Tj
T*
(- JPA repositories perform database operations.) Tj
T*
(- Entity classes map Java objects to database tables.) Tj
T*
(- Spring Security handles authentication and authorization.) Tj
T*
(- JWT service generates and validates tokens.) Tj
