(## CONCLUSION) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The Romify Travel Booking System fulfills the objective of creating a centralized platform for) Tj
T*
(travel booking services. It improves user convenience by combining hotels, flights, buses,) Tj
T*
(booking history, payment workflow, and city guide assistance into one web application.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## SUMMARY / CONCLUSION) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This project demonstrates full-stack application development using Angular, Spring Boot, and) Tj
T*
(MySQL. It includes modular frontend design, REST API development, JWT-based authentication,) Tj
T*
(database integration, and a practical chatbot feature.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## LIMITATIONS OF THE SYSTEM) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Payment gateway is implemented as a workflow screen, not a real payment integration.) Tj
T*
(- Travel inventory is seeded/static and not connected to live suppliers.) Tj
T*
(- Chatbot uses predefined city data and does not call an external AI or tourism API.) Tj
T*
(- Admin management is mainly focused on hotel records.) Tj
T*
(- No email or SMS notification is currently implemented.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj
T*
